    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I see what you mean about letting go, but i dont mean just resting or getting help. i mean like... if life is just a constant loop of suffering, is it actually wrong to just decide it's over? like, is there a point where it's more logical to just stop existing than to keep trying to fix things that are clearly broken?",
